## ℹ️ Credentials

The JMAP standard does not limit the available authentication options. Fastmail (the sponsor of the standard) supports Bearer authentication as well as OAuth2.

In n8n you can implement the Fastmail Bearer authentication by creating Header Auth credentials with a name of `Authorization` and a value of `Bearer $apiToken` (replacing `$apiToken` with your actual [token from Fastmail]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}
